#31107
The Frjosa Hel-vegr Tundra~
   To the north, you can hear the loud roaring of the river.  The snow is very
deep and makes moving very difficult.  Everything is white and cold here.  
The expansive and cruel white abyss settles in one's soul like a profound
hopelessness.  You have exits in all four cardinal directions and all lead to
more snow except the north.  
~
